cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper deals with 3D shape understanding and captioning, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. The proposed method involves a generative caption network, which is a machine learning model, and hence, it can also be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves the detection and segmentation of 3D shapes, which can be considered as a graphics-related task and hence, can be categorized under computer graphics (cs.GR) sub-category.
